Up for sale is a beautifully restored 2007 Regal 2400 open-bow family day-boat in off white with black coves and no bottom paint ever. The boat only has 110 original hours on it, according to the hour meter, and it features a Volvo Penta 5.7 GXi engine yielding 320 prop horsepower with a new Duo Prop outdrive (16 hours of use).
